text: Linda Gary (born Linda Gary Howerton Dewoskin; November 4, 1944 â€“ October 5, 1995) was an American voice actress and voice over artist who did animated projects. She voiced the character of Jane on Tarzan, Lord of the Jungle. In Web Woman, she voiced the title character. Gary was born in California.
